{"tid":757694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞出榴槤味做乜鳩","createTime":"2018-07-27T05:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T07:16:27.000Z","uid":195479,"like":12,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6d1ff8ce8611c65b63f2a17fa7a8dc275adf0a","tid":757694,"uid":195479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"本身對榴槤都冇咩好感，依家麥當勞仲要出咗榴槤味麥旋風，我真係屌撚左一聲，隔個街口都聞到濃烈榴槤味，更何況行過麥當勞，真係臭到仆街。又買得貴，終極特濃版成55蚊，真係痴撚咗線，食杯雪糕仲貴過食餐飯！成班羊群心理，冒住三十幾度，烈日當空之下曬住，條人龍長到打晒蛇餅咁都要買杯咁臭既雪糕雪糕 真係佩服<br />\n你賣雪糕都算 咁多口味唔出 偏偏出隻榴槤口味 搞到成街都係榴槤味，真係好惡頂<br />\n幾時賣撚完佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5903db56ba95b6dafded7466c0450fe78f984795","tid":757694,"uid":60074,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"好味到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b7b959958c91281538c9e783f6aa4b1784550f","tid":757694,"uid":31071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但去到次次賣哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42405c616bb30087cfb9779f40ec50b9afffc50a","tid":757694,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"以前阿波羅d 生果係frozen <br />\n佢d 榴槤放室温, 仲要成日攪, 成日扙黎拔去<br />\n肯定出晒水<br />\n<br />\n食完唔屙有假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要見只係扙一細匙, 連半殼都無, 搵笨柒<br />\n本身想幫襯下<br />\n睇到即時掉頭走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c76771849595410cdb5da64ab157149356dc5d0","tid":757694,"uid":195479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5903db56ba95b6dafded7466c0450fe78f984795","tid":757694,"uid":60074,"like":6,